      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Project car or budget beater opportunity knocking! This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has significant mechanical and/or cosmetic issues that will need some serious attention. It's best suited for a handy buyer, a DIY enthusiast, or someone looking for a parts car. If you've got the skills and the vision, this could be a rewarding project at a wallet-friendly price!",
