    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has significant damage including multiple scratches, dents, and visible rust in several areas. The interior is heavily worn with damaged seating, cracked surfaces, and general deterioration throughout. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues and will likely require substantial repairs. Suitable for parts or a buyer willing to invest in significant restoration work.",
      "price": 5000.0,
